  <body>
    <h1>Add Department</h1>
    <h2>Basic Path</h2>
    <ol>
      <li><p>Include <a href="View-Departments.html">View Departments"</a></p></li>
      <li><p>The use case begins when the Inventory Manager selects "Add Department".</p></li>
      <li><p>The software retrieves the types of units that are being used. </li>
      <li><p>The software retrieves the department names and their corresponding department numbers
	  that are being used.</p></li>
      <li><p>The software finds a default number by adding one to
	     the maxiumum current department number.</p></li>
      <li><p>The software prompts for the department's name, department number
	  and department group.</p></li>
      <li><p>Using the types of units retrieved previously, the software prompts for
	  the department's default unit type.</p></li>
      <li><p>The software checks that the department name and number are unique.</p></li>
      <li><p>The software creates a department using the department name,
	  number, and default unit type.</p><li>
      <li><p>The software updates any listing of departments.</p></li>
    </ol>
    
    <h2>Alternate Paths</h2>
    <h3>DB Error</h3>
